@TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5112

### Get all providers (default pagination: page 1, size 10)
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers
Accept: application/json

###

### Get providers with specific pagination
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Get second page with 5 elements per page
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?pageNumber=2&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

###

### General search (searches in Name, Nit and Email)
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?searchTerm=ejemplo
Accept: application/json

###

### Specific filter by NIT
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?nit=900123
Accept: application/json

###

### Specific filter by Email
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?email=proveedor.com
Accept: application/json

###

### Combined filters: NIT and Email
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?nit=900&email=@proveedor
Accept: application/json

###

### Sort by name (ascending)
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?orderBy=name&orderDescending=false
Accept: application/json

###

### Sort by name (descending)
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?orderBy=name&orderDescending=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Sort by creation date (most recent first)
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?orderBy=createdAt&orderDescending=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Sort by email (ascending)
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?orderBy=email&orderDescending=false
Accept: application/json

###

### Sort by NIT (descending)
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?orderBy=nit&orderDescending=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Search with pagination and sorting
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?searchTerm=proveedor&pageNumber=1&pageSize=15&orderBy=name&orderDescending=false
Accept: application/json

###

### Filter by NIT with pagination and sorting
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?nit=900&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&orderBy=createdAt&orderDescending=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Complete example: search + filters + pagination + sorting
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?searchTerm=ejemplo&nit=900&pageNumber=1&pageSize=20&orderBy=name&orderDescending=false
Accept: application/json

###

### Get providers with large pagination (useful for export)
GET {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/providers?pageNumber=1&pageSize=100
Accept: application/json

